      <h2 class="section-title">Two building blocks. <span class="gradient-text">One platform.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">TCS is made up of two kinds of building blocks: <strong>Platform Services</strong> — the back-office engine and brains — and <strong>Mobile Applications</strong> — the tools your team uses every day. The services power the apps, and AI is woven through both.</p>
    </div>

