    <!-- Building block 1: Platform Services -->
    <div class="layer-block">
      <div class="layer-head">
        <span class="layer-tag">Building block 1</span>
        <h3 class="layer-title">Platform Services</h3>
        <p class="layer-desc">Your back-office engine and the brains behind the mobile and web front ends. These shared services manage product information, customer accounts, identity, and security — and power the apps your team uses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-grid-3">
        <a href="/platform/pxp/" class="svc-card">
          <div class="svc-shot"><i class="ti ti-box"></i></div>
          <div class="svc-body">
            <h3 class="svc-title">PXP — Product Experience Platform</h3>
            <p class="svc-desc">Centralized product information — the single place product data lives. Manage product details, variants, and enrichments so accurate, consistent product data flows across your business.</p>
            <div class="svc-plus">
              <div class="svc-plus-head"><span class="svc-plus-badge">PLUS</span><span class="svc-plus-lbl">Adds</span></div>
              <div class="svc-plus-list">AI Empowerment · Product Discovery · Product Training</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/platform/cxp/" class="svc-card">
          <div class="svc-shot"><i class="ti ti-users"></i></div>
          <div class="svc-body">
            <h3 class="svc-title">CXP — Customer Experience Platform</h3>
            <p class="svc-desc">The central platform for managing customer data and the system of record for your customer relationships — a complete upgrade to Secure CRM. Customer self-registration improves data quality and cuts manual account setup at the store, with multinational support and cleansed customer data.</p>
            <div class="svc-plus">
              <div class="svc-plus-head"><span class="svc-plus-badge">PLUS</span><span class="svc-plus-lbl">Adds</span></div>
              <div class="svc-plus-list">AI Empowerment · Discovery Session History · 121 Clienteling</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/platform/tap/" class="svc-card">
          <div class="svc-shot"><i class="ti ti-shield-lock"></i></div>
          <div class="svc-body">
            <h3 class="svc-title">TAP — Teamwork Administration Platform</h3>
            <p class="svc-desc">The secure administrative layer for the platform. TAP manages authentication and authorization, employee account access, and workforce management — controlling who can do what, safely. Includes user &amp; role management, QR-code authentication, and single sign-on through TEAMMATE.</p>
            <div class="svc-plus">
              <div class="svc-plus-head"><span class="svc-plus-badge">PLUS</span><span class="svc-plus-lbl">Adds</span></div>
              <div class="svc-plus-list">AI Empowerment · Product Training · Operational Training</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Building block 2: Mobile Applications -->
    <div class="layer-block">
      <div class="layer-head">
        <span class="layer-tag">Building block 2</span>
        <h3 class="layer-title">Mobile Applications</h3>
        <p class="layer-desc">The tools for your store associates' day-to-day operations — TEAMMATE for associates and POS for store operations, both running on the same platform services.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-grid-2">
        <a href="/platform/teammate/" class="svc-card">
          <div class="svc-shot"><i class="ti ti-id-badge-2"></i></div>
          <div class="svc-body">
            <h3 class="svc-title">TEAMMATE</h3>
            <p class="svc-desc">The app for store associates — secure mobile access to the tools they use throughout the day, starting with secure login based on rotating QR codes on iOS and Android.</p>
            <div class="svc-plus">
              <div class="svc-plus-head"><span class="svc-plus-badge">PLUS</span><span class="svc-plus-lbl">Adds</span></div>
              <div class="svc-plus-list">AI Empowerment · Product Discovery · Product Training · Operational Training</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/platform/mobile-pos/" class="svc-card">
