            <p class="svc-desc">Modern point of sale, built on TCS. POS handles retail transactions while connecting associates to the wider platform — one app, tied to the same product, customer, and identity data.</p>
            <div class="svc-plus">
              <div class="svc-plus-head"><span class="svc-plus-badge">PLUS</span><span class="svc-plus-lbl">Adds</span></div>
              <div class="svc-plus-list">AI Empowerment · Product Discovery · 121 Clienteling</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
